3. The Birthday Party (18 September 1969)  
Jimmy is disappointed as it is his birthday and nobody knows. Pufnstuf and Pop Lolly decide to give Jimmy a surprise 
birthday party.  Witchiepoo crashes the party as "The Three Lemons" group, and blows laughing gas over everyone, and in the choas steals Freddy.
(Episdode 7 on H.R. Pufnstuf The Complete Series DVD)
